description: The Deka DAX ex Financials 30 UCITS ETF is a UCITS IV-compliant mutual fund that replicates the performance of the DAX ex Financials 30 Index (price index). The index includes the 30 largest companies from the regulated market of the Frankfurt Stock Exchange (FWB) that do not belong to the financial services, insurance, or real estate sectors. The DAX Index rules apply for inclusion in the index.
name: Deka DAX ex Financials 30 UCITS ETF
